nd enhancing perception. Together, these diverse virtual environments suggest the many ways that video games enhance and extend our embodied lives.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aPlace (Philosophy) in art. 0aPlace (Philosophy) in mass media. 0aVideo gamesxDesign. 4aArchitektur. 4aBuilt Environment. 4aEmbodied Cognition. 4aKommunikation. 4aVideospiele. 7aHISTORY / Study & Teaching.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2022 Englishz978311099296008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2022z9783110992939oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831107238470 cprintz978311072357140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311072373140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110723731423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110723731/original  a978-3-11-099296-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022